title: #92Noon! Leber/Rosas/Gleeman
description: Ben Leber in studio right out of the gates with Vikings conversation throughout the first hour. Wolves PBO Gersson Rosas pumps up the season opener, with more NFL and new nuggets taking you to the final hour with Gleeman in studio on baseball and hoops.
